<span weight='bold' size='xx-large'>Organization</span>

The <b>Organization</b> of a contact is specifically where they are from, for example:
<b>Microsoft</b>
<b>U.S Army</b>
<b>Harvard University</b>
<b>Local High School</b>

Just like the <b>Name</b> field, the <b>Organization</b> field can be left blank,
and any input is valid.
